  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Better Mill Initiative</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The overall programme objective is to improve the sustainability performance of textile wet processing in the fashion supply chain in China.&#xA0; The Yangtze River Delta and Pearl River Delta are key geographical textile clusters. The project aims to move beyond compliance through a systems based approach to continuous improvement. The project is a collaboration between the Sustainable Apparel Coalition, ZDHC, BCI and Solidaridad. It allows for alignment and experience sharing to contribute to existing standards and tools.</narrative>
  </description>
